      "description": "Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a truly mint-condition vehicle! This car is in exceptional shape inside and out \u2014 the paintwork is flawless and gleaming, the interior is spotless and fresh, and every mechanical component is performing beautifully. It's clear this car has been meticulously cared for, and it shows in every detail. Whether you're looking for a reliable daily driver or a head-turning ride you'll be proud to own, this one checks every box. Come see it for yourself \u2014 you won't be disappointed!",
