    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used-car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. The paint retains a deep, factory-fresh shine that turns heads. The interior is equally impressive: every surface is clean, unmarked, and well-preserved, with no wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or trim. All electronics, controls, and features function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission \u2014 are in top-notch working order. This is a vehicle you can buy with full confidence, knowing it has been exceptionally well cared for. Serious buyers will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46500.0,
