      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a good-condition car. Buyers can expect a well-maintained example that presents nicely and drives reliably, though it does show some signs of normal use and age. The exterior is in good shape overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear that you'd expect from a used vehicle \u2014 nothing severe or structurally concerning. The paint retains most of its luster, and the body panels are straight with no significant dents. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces like the steering wheel and door handles, but no major tears, stains, or damage. All primary features and controls work as intended. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been kept up with regular maintenance; buyers should still plan for a pre-purchase inspection, as with any used vehicle. This is a solid, honest, everyday driver that offers good value for someone looking for a dependable used car without paying mint-condition prices.",
